message: Dear Bob, I am excited to offer you our premium product, which is valued at $15000. Considering its exceptional quality and unique features, I believe it would greatly benefit you. To ensure we both reach an agreeable deal, I propose a price of $14500. This offer includes a comprehensive warranty and a personalized setup service to ensure seamless integration into your operations. Please let me know if this proposal meets your expectations, or if you require further details. Looking forward to your positive response.
